{
  "stem": "11844.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No point in going into details.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, a terrible thing occurred, and it was the first time in my life that I had an opportunity to do something wonderful.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In January, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 1940, Sonja got a use certificate for Aliyah to Israel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The war was five months old-- started in August; we are now in January-- and she did not want to go to Israel in January, '40, because she wanted to be with me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I somehow sensed or believed that eventually, the Nazis will Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Holland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean Holland, which actually happened on May 10, 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I tried every type of persuasion on Sonja to accept her possibility to go to Israel and she didn't.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I called her very bad names, which I cannot repeat here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did everything possible to push her away from me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Didn't.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I beat her up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the first time in my life that I did something great and put her interest over-- for me, to l-- lose her was terrible, by the way.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I felt that I-- she had to go because she could save her life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And probably, she couldn't do it in Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until today, she is very much in my heart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was afterwards.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The camp was, at that time, run by an Israeli gentlemen by the name of Moise Katznelson, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] with whom I had a tremendous fight and won.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a soccer team.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was only interested before I came to the camp, where-- which was my college, with gambling, girls, and soccer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing else really interested me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had a soccer team there, and we were playing a little bit around.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
